{"tid":802548,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國記者分享逃離 Google 方法！中國網民：你搬來中國就可以了","createTime":"2018-09-01T13:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T14:57:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a2aeab0277ab2f012c625331be7cf54ed37eaa1","tid":802548,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/s_f6f83b8ff51948d982a98f24496ebc9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fs_f6f83b8ff51948d982a98f24496ebc9e.jpg&h=5595ecf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今時今日智能電話主要分為 Android 及 iOS 系統，而在我日常的生活中，Google 服務似乎已經是生活的必需品之一。大家嘅 Android 系統，Gmail 電郵，看地圖時用 Google Maps，搜尋時用的 Google Search 等等。<br />\n不過有一名外國記者就認為，Google 出現在生活中的每一個角落，反而令人感到恐懼。故此，他花了足足半年的時間，去嚐試遠離所有 Google 服務，順便亦放棄了 Facebook。<br />\n在他分享的文章中，他向其他人介紹了種種能夠替代 Google 的方案，當然是不是最好的選擇就各花入各眼了。而在花了半年時間後，他亦終於用種種不同的方式取代所有 Google 服務於日常生活之中。<br />\n<br />\n對於他的毅力，網民有不同的意見。有人認為科技進步，沒必要如此規限自己。不過更有趣的是，大批中國網民認為，作者只需要搬到中國就可以，根本不需要花半年。莫非真的是「牆入面的人想出來，牆外面的人想入去？」"},{"pid":"7438481dbcd1eeb79c30f90cb23cafac97216d26","tid":802548,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"神回"},{"pid":"d1c1b6ed09099415857110d63139321876534f9b","tid":802548,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"中國真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794faecd08110220bf8866481c7198d230e55944","tid":802548,"uid":54904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"黎中國咪又係比中共監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aabc0ec01c3a4ed0b06e59f7e628ff9b041c7d3","tid":802548,"uid":60665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"